text: Welcome.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele

text: Thank you for having me.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t73.96000000000001
text: I'm very excited to be here.

id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t74.96000000000001
text: I think we first met back in 2018 when you were at Winfield United and we did a webinar

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t79.64
text: together about data and analytics.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t82.32
text: Now you're at the parent company, Land O'Lakes.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t84.63999999999999
text: Can you tell us about your current role?

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t86.19999999999999
text: Yeah, absolutely.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t87.19999999999999
text: So I'm the chief technology officer here at Land O'Lakes and it's a farmer owned cooperative,

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t93.24
text: farm to fork cooperative, I would say as well.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t95.6
text: We cover the whole gamut all the way from the time the seed goes into the ground, crops

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t100.0
text: come out of the ground, they turn into grain, right?

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t103.61999999999999
text: The grain then is used for animal feed and Purina is also a Land O'Lakes brand.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t108.32
text: And so that grain is then used to create feed formulations for animals.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t113.39999999999999
text: And then those dairy producers are part of the cooperative.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t116.8
text: We buy the milk from those producers and turn it into value added products such as butter

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t121.16
text: and cheese, which you find at the store.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t123.55999999999999
text: So when we talk farm to fork, you truly cover the whole spectrum here in a very large way.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t130.48
text: And my responsibility as a chief technology officer is obviously anything that runs the

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t134.8
text: internal systems for our organization, you know, enterprises for planning ERP websites,

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t139.76000000000002
text: CRM, things like that.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t141.56
text: But another exciting area is the area of data and analytics as well as a lot of software

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t148.0
text: that's used actually in our business working with our customers, whether it's supporting

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t153.02
text: an existing business model or helping develop a new business model that then runs on the

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t157.88000000000002
text: technology and really working with those business leaders to be able to define what that is

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t162.96
text: and then working either with internal resources or with external third parties to be able

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t167.16
text: to develop some really neat solutions.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t170.12
text: And the composition of the co-op is what?

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t173.56
text: It's really interesting.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t174.56
text: So the co-op is made up of two sides of the membership.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t177.26000000000002
text: One I mentioned a second ago, they're dairy producers.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t179.48000000000002
text: And that is how the company got started.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t181.72
text: Exactly 101 years ago, dairy producers here in Minnesota got together and said, we want

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t186.86
text: to get our product out east.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t189.04000000000002
text: And so they created this cooperative to be able to handle more of an aggregation of all

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t192.6
text: their products.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t193.84
text: The other side of the membership are ag retailers.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t196.76
text: And so these are independently and operated businesses in rural communities.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t201.51999999999998
text: And they serve row crop farmers, predominantly row crop farmers in those communities.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t206.4
text: So corn, soybeans, wheat, canola.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t210.06
text: And what we do for them is as a supply cooperative, we buy the large seed crop protection products

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t215.79999999999998
text: from large manufacturers and we sell it to them and then they sell it to the farmers

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t219.56
text: that they serve.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t220.88
text: And in a lot of cases, these ag retailers are also cooperatives themselves.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t224.1
text: So their boards are made up of the farmers they serve.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t227.88
text: So our board is made up of half of these dairy producers and the other half is these ag retailers.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t233.28
text: And that combination is the Land O'Lakes cooperative.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t237.16
text: And as the CTO, what's your mandate for the co-op?

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t241.32
text: We are here to serve the members all the way down to that row crop farmer and making sure

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t246.54
text: that we make them competitive at the farm gate, whatever they need to do on a day to

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t250.51999999999998
text: day basis to stay competitive.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t252.57999999999998
text: And particularly as a chief technology officer, how do we keep up with the latest trends?

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t256.5
text: How do we make sure we apply those technology trends to the solutions we give them?

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t261.44
text: How do we make our supply chain more efficient?

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t264.18
text: And really I'd be here for another hundred years to make sure that we're successful.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t268.78
text: And technology has been transforming the ag business from what I understand.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t272.88
text: Can you just give one on one of that to our audience?

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t276.24
text: So they get a sense of how is technology really changing the agriculture and farming business?

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t283.22
text: It's one of the oldest industries in the world.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t286.46000000000004
text: And for hundreds, maybe thousands of years, it was done exactly the same way.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t291.56
text: And in the last hundred years, you've had some tremendous changes from starting with

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t296.04
text: the tractor.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t297.04
text: And all of a sudden things get a little more automated.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t299.68
text: When crop protection was introduced, that was a big deal.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t302.9
text: When you did all this work, it could all be gone because of some pestilence that occurred

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t306.84
text: on the field.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t307.96
text: The next piece was the biotech revolution.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t310.96
text: And so now there's a lot more research and a lot more technology that went into the seed

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t315.79999999999995
text: that goes into the ground.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t316.79999999999995
text: And could it be drought resistant?

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t318.84
text: Could it still come out of the ground when it's too wet?

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t321.21999999999997
text: Could it be resistant to certain diseases?

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t323.46
text: And that was a big game changer.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t325.21999999999997
text: And so you call it kind of the third revolution.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t327.06
text: But this fourth revolution agriculture is now the application of technology, and particularly

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t332.58
text: software technology to ag from simple things of just being able to run descriptive analytics

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t339.14
text: to various components of artificial intelligence.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t343.09999999999997
text: And it's I mean, this fourth one, though, it's put agriculture in a hyperdrive because

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t348.08
text: all of a sudden you're starting to see all this complex environment that really was managed

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t353.29999999999995
text: with intuition.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t354.94
text: And now your productivity goes up.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t357.15999999999997
text: Now data and the technology is really helping you through this.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t359.78
text: So you're more and more reliant on data coming off the field and then making decisions.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t365.28
text: That really is the change in what's happening in the agriculture today.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t369.21999999999997
text: And that data is really massive, right?

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t371.05999999999995
text: I mean, many different sources, many different permutations, right?

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t376.17999999999995
text: There are so many things that happen from obviously you have weather, which is a big

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t381.02
text: component in agriculture.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t382.82

id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t387.24

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t400.6

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t403.96000000000004
text: So you have all that variability that happens.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t406.64

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t411.2

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t415.52
text: Then there's the selection of the right type of seed.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t418.64
text: You've got to take that into account.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t420.08
text: And then we talked about applying nutrients and applying crop protection.

title: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele
id: Big Data in Agriculture - Land O'Lakes' Teddy Bekele-t423.35999999999996
